In dictum in enim sit amet mattis. Sed sagittis mauris et viverra viverra.

Donec tincidunt velit eu massa lobortis consequat. Etiam vitae volutpat enim. Vivamus placerat mattis dignissim. Nullam diam nisl, posuere a turpis sit amet, efficitur vestibulum dolor. Fusce arcu arcu, suscipit sit amet feugiat.

Policy"][vc_empty_space height="3em" alter_height="none" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ul class="trx_addons_list trx_addons_list_dot">
 	<li>To get a pre-purchase advice, you may post in the theme’s forum.</li>
 	<li>To get a response more promptly, you are recommended to use our Ticket-system.</li>
 	<li>We try to answer your questions within 1-10 hours. However, if any delay occurs, it doesn’t mean that we forgot about you. Some of the issues require testing and analyzing, so we can resolve it effectively.</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ul class="trx_addons_list trx_addons_list_dot">
 	<li>Please note! We do not provide support, if you do not have the purchase code.</li>
 	<li>Item support does not include:
<ol>
 	<li>Customization and installation.</li>
 	<li>Support for third party software and plugins.</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_align="center" title="How to use our Support System"][vc_empty_space height="4em" alter_height="none" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="116" img_size="large"][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ol>
 	<li>In the ‘Item Details’ there is a clickable banner “Support Sys”, which leads you to tickets.</li>
 	<li>Or you may simply follow this link: <a href="https://ancorathemes.ticksy.com/">ancorathemes.ticksy.com</a>.</li>
 	<li>Enter your purchase key and register in the system.</li>
 	<li>To avoid a confusion, please use your own ThemeForest login in Support System.</li>
 	<li>Fill out the ticket form.</li>
</ol>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_align="center" title="How to find a purchase key"][vc_empty_space height="4em" alter_height="none" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="117" img_size="large"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ol>
 	<li>Open the “downloads” tab in your account.</li>
 	<li>Find our theme in the list of products.</li>
 	<li>Click “download” button, and in the drop-down menu select “license certificate &amp; purchase code”.</li>
</ol>

In that case, you are always welcome to contact our support team to get qualified help."][vc_empty_space height="4em" alter_height="none" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="118" img_size="large" alignment="center"][vc_column_text]
